snippet.title: Best VGM 2315 - Castlevania : Bloodlines - Sinking Old Sanctuary
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 887 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U9z3oWS0Qo0
Best VGM 1684 - http://youtu.be/2mlPgPBDovw

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Genesis
Castlevania : Bloodlines (1994)
Sinking Old Sanctuary (Stage 2)
Michiru Yamane
